CloudFlare,provides,fast,and,secure,content,delivery,network,for,websites,and,applications,The,CloudFlare,API,exposes,CloudFlare,infrastructure,by,using,a,standardized,programmatic,interface,With,the,RESTful,CloudFlare,API,developers,can,send,HTTP,requests,and,receive,JSON,responses,to,integrate,security,domains,and,hosting,features